      "content": "hey i just got this prescription for zolpidem for my sleeping issues but im having a really hard time drifting off. been having a glass of red wine with dinner lately and was wondering if it's okay to take the pill with the wine? i feel like it might actually help the med kick in faster so i dont lay there awake all night",
